	<dt>vote for tony get Gordon (and a whole...</dt>
	<dd><p>vote for tony get Gordon (and a whole new lexicon of untruths).....vote for Mike and get second prize again....vote for Chaz and watch the taxes rise (at least he is honest about it) </p>
	<small>
